    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Describes the culture and style of a group of Australian Aboriginal peoples whose ancestral land is located in Arnhem Land, in the present-day Northern Territory. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
